results.title: Typst
results.description: Typst is a new markup-based typesetting system for the sciences, designed as a highly capable and user-friendly alternative to tools like LaTeX, Word, and Google Docs.

results.title: Typst Algo
results.description: Typst Algo is a Typst library for writing algorithms, providing functions for creating pseudocode and code blocks with various styling options.

results.title: Tinymist
results.description: Tinymist is an integrated language service for Typst, providing a CLI, language server (LSP), and editor integrations with features such as semantic highlighting, formatting, document preview, and various export options.
